textBox.richText: Add another two people to the million or so that visit each year. Flick and I conquered ‘The Rock’. We took the first ferry over and spent the morning enjoying the sights. Unfortunately I felt the effects of the dodgy curry and had to use the conveniences in one of the cells. Felicity saw it as a good opportunity to embarrass me by taking a happy snap during the evacuation process!! How rude! :)
